382.name: A Forest Trail
desc: "   The trees around you are old, tall and gnarly.  This
is an ancient grove, the trees covered in moss, their roots
exposed as the soil has settled over the years.  To the
east you can see what appears to be a road, though a trail

397.name: Deep in the Mountains
desc: "   You are deep in the mountains.  The granite peaks
stretch to the sky all around you.  In the distance you
can see some smoking volcanoes, signs of the recent
past of this land.  You need to tread carefully here
as the trails are covered with recent landslides and
the gorges are at hand to welcome any careless traveller
to their depths.  A trail lies to the north, leading
up the edge of a mountain.
